headline.main: Banks Could Earn $332 Million From Wave of Financial Services Deals
headline.print_headline: Banks Could Earn $332 Million From Wave of Financial Services Deals

lead_paragraph: A spate of big deals by financial services companies in Europe could earn investment banks an estimated $332 million in advisory fees, with Goldman Sachs set to take the lion's share of the pot.
